snippet.title: Wardens Rising Developer Interview - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Big Moxi Games dropped by the Future Games Show Expansion Pack to dig into Wardens Rising. It's a spacefaring, genre-blending bonanza, an ARPG shooter that grafts in MOBA and tower defence elements.  It's coming soon to PC and consoles. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #Wardensrising #gamescom
